\lim_{x\rightarrow1}\frac{\frac{1}{\sqrt{x}}-1}{x-1}
\lim_{x\rightarrow1}\dfrac{\dfrac{1-\sqrt{x}}{\sqrt{x}}}{x-1}
\lim_{x\rightarrow1}\dfrac{1-\sqrt{x}}{\sqrt{x}}\cdot\dfrac{1}{x-1}
\lim_{x\rightarrow1}\dfrac{1-\sqrt{x}}{x\sqrt{x}-\sqrt{x}}
0
y=\sqrt{x}
x\rightarrow 1
y\rightarrow 1
\lim_{x\rightarrow 1}{ \frac{1-\sqrt{x}}{x\sqrt{x}-\sqrt{x}}}= \lim_{y\rightarrow 1}{\frac{1-y}{y^3-y}}=\lim_{y\rightarrow 1}{\frac{-(y-1)}{y(y-1)(y+1)}}=\lim_{y\rightarrow 1}{\frac{-1}{y(y+1)}}=-\frac{1}{2}
\lim_{x\rightarrow 1}\frac{\frac{1}{\sqrt{x}}-1}{x-1}= \lim_{x\rightarrow 1}\frac{1-\sqrt{x}}{\sqrt{x}(x-1)}\cdot\frac{1+\sqrt{x}}{1+\sqrt{x}}=\lim_{x\rightarrow 1}\frac{1-x}{(x-1)\sqrt{x}(1+\sqrt{x})}=
=\lim_{x\rightarrow 1}-\frac{x-1}{\sqrt{x}(x-1)(1+\sqrt{x})}=\lim_{x\rightarrow 1}-\frac{1}{\sqrt{x}(1+\sqrt{x})}=-\frac{1}{2}. 
